p           play / pause
f           toggle fullscreen
m           toggle mute
v           toggle subtitles
s           screenshot
shift + s   screenshot w/o subtitles
ctrl + c    quit
q           quit, save current position
o           show progress
shift + o   toggle show progress
page up     next chapter
page down   previous chapter
.           next frame
,           previous frame
ctrl +      increase audio delay
ctrl -      decrease audio delay
[           decrease speed
]           increase speed
1           decrease contrast
2           increase contrast
3           decrease brightness
4           increase brightness
5           decrease gamma
6           increase gamma
7           decrease saturation
8           increase saturation
9           decrease audio volume
0           increase audio volume
w           zoom out
e           zoom in
